df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1067532</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:20:56.000Z","msg":"Long live yellow uncle! 黃伯一定長命百歲，闔家平安！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}